#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/standard-deviation.md:13
msgid ""
"`standard_deviation` restituisce la deviazione standard come radice quadrata della varianza "
"calcolata da [`variance`](variance.md)."
msgstr ""
"`standard_deviation` returns the standard deviation as the square root of the variance computed "
"by [`variance`](variance.md)."

